<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-159-167 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 738 011</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  May 6 1991 v8 n18 p22(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Radley-EDI release 2 lets DECscheduler create commands.andO;(Electronic data interchange) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Briggs, George.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Rand Systems Corp. Radley Business Computers (Productintroduction).andO;Product:   Radley-EDI 2 (Communications software) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Electronic Data InterchangeProduct IntroductionSoftware Packages.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Radley-EDI release 2 lets DECscheduler create commandsandM;SOUTHFIELD, Mich.andP;  -- Radley Business Computers has announced that Radley-EDIrelease 2 is now callable via DECscheduler management software.andP;  Release 2also lets developers and consultants call EDI modules from within theirapplications, Radley officials said.andM;&quot;Now you can create commands that will be invoked from DECscheduler toinitiate the EDI process,&quot; said Will Soutar, Radley's EDI product manager.andO;In addition, software developers, consultants and end users now have theability to call EDI modules from within their applications.andM;Written for VAX/VMS, the software has document translation, mapping andcommunications bundled within it, eliminating the need to purchase separatemodules to address each function, the officials said.andM;The software's mapping function allows users to customize the integration ofinhouse applications with the trading-partner specifications of inbound oroutbound EDI documents.andM;Flat files or user-defined files can be tailored to fit a programming style,such as Cobol record typing or multiple file types, via mapping.andP;  A modelingfunction lets users create outbound EDI documents based on a tradingpartner's requirements, using the ANSI X12 standard or another partner'sdocument as the base model.andP;  Inbound EDI translation dictionaries are createdin the same way.andM;Radley-EDI translation and communication modules can be run interactively, inbatch mode or via DECscheduler, the officials said.andM;Radley-EDI release 2 is available now.andP;  Prices start at $1,995 for a one- totwo-company Trading Partner License and range to $28,000 for an UnlimitedTrading Partner License.andM;Radley Business Computers Inc. is located at 23077 Greenfield, Suite 440,Southfield, MI 48075, (800) 334-9934.andO;</TEXT></DOC>